>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=219390\">Gaviota - FM Miguel A. Ballicora - live at ICC in 1 hour</a> by <a href=\"/Peter_Berger\" title=\"Peter Berger\">Peter Berger</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 24, 2002</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=221364\">Great article for people who wants to write a chess engine</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Miguel A. Ballicora</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 03, 2002 <sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2005_...\">2005 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Miguel_A._Ballicora&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2005 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=21119\">Move ordering: Delaying moves on the history phase</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Miguel A. Ballicora</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 13, 2008&#160;» <a href=\"/index.php?title=Move_ordering&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Move ordering (page does not exist)\">Move ordering</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=27266\">Insanity... or Tal style?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Miguel A. Ballicora</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 01, 2009</li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=27266&amp;postdays=0&amp;postorder=asc&amp;topic_view=&amp;start=11\">Re: Insanity... or Tal style?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Miguel A. Ballicora</a>,