\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=41938\">Ordo release (rating software, ELO-like)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Miguel A. Ballicora</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 11, 2012</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=52661\">UCI, ownbooks, and a potential problem</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Miguel A. Ballicora</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 16, 2014&#160;» <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a>, <a href=\"/Opening_Book\" title=\"Opening Book\">Opening Book</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=53645\">Ordo 0.9.6</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Miguel A. Ballicora</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 10, 2014</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Miguel_A._Ballicora&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=59038\">Ordo 1.0.9 (new features for testers)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Miguel A. Ballicora</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 25, 2016</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=59388\">Ordoprep 0.8</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Miguel A. Ballicora</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 28, 2016</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Miguel_A._Ballicora&amp;act